@node "keyfile" "How to get a free KeyFile"
@{PAR}@{LINE}
 @{b}@{u}How to get a FREE KeyFile@{ub}@{uu}
@{PAR}@{LINE}
 There is no excuse not to register this program if you use it.
 It's 100% FREE and to get a keyfile just e-mail the @{"Author" link "author"0}
 and don't forget to include your name.

 Q: Why do I need a keyfile ?

 A: Keyfile has been added for one single reason,
    and it is to see how many people using this program.

 @{b}@{u}Limits without keyfile@{ub}@{uu}

 The program is fully functional except for 3 things.

 You can't use the "Read" "Write" "Delete" functions
 in main window.

 @{b}I've noticed a cracked version of MP3-TagED v2.3 (cracked by zIgUS/FTN)
 If you are using a cracked keyfile then please delete it and get one from the 
 author instead, or else this may be the last version.
 @{ub}

 ---------------------------------------------------------------------

 Your name will only be used to create a keyfile for your own personal
 use. The keyfile will be sent to you as soon as possible.

@endnode

@node "howtoinstall" "Installation"
@{PAR}@{LINE}
 @{u}Installation@{uu}

 Use the supplied Installer script.



 The following files should be in the MP3TEDv26.lha archive.

 @{u}File                        @{uu} @{u}Description                   @{uu}
 file_id.diz                  File description.
 MP3-TagED.info               Drawer icon.
 @{fg highlight}MP3-TagED/@{fg text}
   Install                    Installation script.
   Install.info               Installation script icon.
   @{fg highlight}Libs/@{fg text}
     gtlayout.library         Library.
     popupmenu.library        Library.
     reqtools.library         Library.
   MP3-TagED                  MP3-TagED - the main program
   MP3-TagED.info             MP3-TagED - icon.
   MP3-TagED.config           Example configuration file.
   MP3-TagED.guide            Documentation file.
   MP3-TagED.guide.info       Documentation file icon.
   READ-ME-FIRST.txt          Read this one first :)
@endnode

