@node "history" "History"
@{PAR}@{LINE}
 @{b}@{u}History@{ub}@{uu}

 @{b}v1.0@{ub} (21-Jul-98)

       @{b}-@{ub} First public release.


 @{b}v2.0@{ub} (25-Oct-98)

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Total rewrite of program.


 @{b}v2.1@{ub} (21-Mar-99)

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} MP3 Header Information - Supported fields:
              - ID
              - Layer
              - BitRate
              - Frequency
              - Mode
              - Length
              - FrameSize

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Added support for AppIcon/AppWindow (Drag-n-Drop).
       
       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Menu items 

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Default MP3-TAG 

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Copy Tag Fields

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} More fields added to Comment FOrmat.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Removed the `Use' button in Preferences window.

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} Rename function was not working properly (fixed).


 @{b}v2.2@{ub} (18-Apr-99)

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} MenuItem Sort - Sort main list by:
              - Filename
              - Artist
              - Songname
              - Album
              - Filesize

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} @{"Status" link "statuswindow" 0} window. (MP3 Info).

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} @{"Genre Status" link "genrestatuswindow" 0} window. (Genre Statistics).

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} @{"KeyFile" link "keyfile" 0} Get it! :)

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Rewrote some parts of Argument parser code.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} The only way to save Default TAG settings is by
                 using the Save button in Preferences window.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} MP3 Information window is replaced by a reqtools requester.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Structure of Preferences file changed.

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} Forgot to free Memory when "Remove" button was pressed.

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} Fixed some errors in the Documentation.

  
 @{b}v2.3@{ub} (3-May-99)

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Installer script finally ready.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} 1 Icon added to the program.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} @{"Known Bugs" link "knownbugs"0} added to MP3-TagED.guide.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Genre button added to Default TAG.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Added Import Playlist - Supported formats:
              -SongPlayer
              -AmigaAMP
              -Amplifier

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Added @{"popupmenu.library." link "popupmenu"0}.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} It's now possible to load a playlist at startup.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Added SKIPPLST - See @{"Arguments" link "arguments" 0}/@{"ToolTypes" link "tooltypes" 0}.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Information window position is now configurable.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} "Tag To FileName" window is removed and replaced with
                 a @{"popupmenu" link "popupmenu"0}.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} "Comment Format" window is also removed and replaced 
                 with a @{"popupmenu" link "popupmenu"0}.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Start button in @{"Copy Tag Fields" link "copytagwindow" 0} window is now disabled.
                 if no fields are marked.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} "Information" requester is replaced by a window (again!).
                 The main reason for this is that you can have the window open
                 and browse the loaded files at the same time. Information will
                 be updated when you select a file.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Cosmetic change made to @{"Status" link "statuswindow" 0} window.
                 (Listview removed and replaced with a @{"gtlayout.library" link "gtlayout" 0} button.

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} "Make FileName From TAG" and "Rename" wasn't working correctly.
                     Forbidden characters will be corrected automaticly.

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} Sort filenames wasn't working correctly. If files from
                    different drawers was loaded the filename wasn't sorted
                    correctly.


 @{b}v2.4@{ub} (27-May-99)

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Percentage now shows in @{"Genre Status" link "genrestatuswindow" 0} window.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} It's now possible to add files by directory.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Pressing TAB when Information window is open will make
               MP3-TagED shift between Main- and Informationwindow.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Information window menuitem is now disabled when Information
               window is open.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Pressing "Add" in @{"Mainwindow" link "mainwindow" 0} and a popupmenu will appear.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Removed the following menuitems:
                 - File /áImport / SongPlayer
                 - File /áImport / Amplifier
                 - File /áImport / AmigaAMP

                 They are replaced with @{"Load PlayList" link "file_import_playlist" 0}
                 All lists can be loaded anyway.

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} "Tag To FileName" wasn't working correctly.
                    The "Space To Underscore" option was always enabled.

                    Reported by: Matt Sawyer (Thanks!)


 @{b}v2.5@{ub} (5-Sep-99)

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Format of Export / Ascii & AmigaGuide is now configurable.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} New prefs window is used for Export / Ascii & AmigaGuide.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} A new menuitem have been added: [Save Settings].

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Filename length is now max 30 characters.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Add directory is removed. No use to have it since aal files can
                 be selected in filerequester. (Lot's of people didn't get it to work).

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Structure of Preferences file changed.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Large parts of Prefs handler is rewritten.

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} Removed enforcer hit on exit.


 @{b}v2.6@{ub} (31-Oct-99)

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} TextViewer is now configurable (Ascii/AmigaGuide preview).

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} There is no need to define X/Y positions for Information window.

              Just move [Test] window and the Left-/TopEdge values will
              automaticually appear.

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} Import / PlayList was "ghosted" when no files was loaded.

 @{b}v2.7@{ub} (5-Jan-2000)

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} AmigaGuide documentation updated.

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Import @{"ACDB" link "file_import_acdb" 0}@{LINE} Files function is now finally ready.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Prefs Handler rewritten again.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Status Handler rewritten.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Delete TAG Window removed and replaced with reqtools-requester.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Popupmenu removed from Write button, Write Select & Write ALL
                 moved to Menu.

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} Year 2000 Bug fixed, correct year will now be written in
                  the Export List functions.

 @{b}v2.8@{ub} (30-Jan-2000)

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} `Copyright' now shows in information window.

              Suggested by: Andy Thomson

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} If program is already running and only 1 is copy allowed,
              another copy can pop up the original program's interface
              or terminate it.

              @{b}This function may contain bugs.@{ub}

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Cosmetic Change made to Settings Window.

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Cosmetic change made to Copy Tag Fields window.
                 (It looks very nice and is more useful in my opinion :)

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} GUI updates here and there.

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} Minor error fixed in the `Delete Tag' function.

 @{b}v2.9@{ub} (27-Feb-2000) (Author's 20'th birthday :)

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} It is now possible to sort the main list by `Path'

              Suggested by: Allan Folmersen

       @{b}- NEW:@{ub} Finally got an Icon in NewIcons style.

              Thanks: Piotr Bartkowiak

       @{b}- CHANGE:@{ub} Minor updates made on the following function:

     á           "If program is already running and only 1 is copy allowed,
                 another copy can pop up the original program's interface
                 or terminate it."

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} The AmigaGuide Edit string in Prefs window wasn't working.

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} AsciiPreview wasn't working correctly.
                  The `temporary' file was deleted before it was viewed.

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} Temporary file from ASCII/AmigaGuide Preview is now deleted
                  at program exit.

       @{b}- BUG-FIX:@{ub} Export output was wrong, it said MP3-TagED v2.7 when it was
                  supposed to be MP3-TagED v2.8.

@endnode

